          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/42098358-archer-s-voice">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/47207032-chelsea-humphrey?shelf=buddy-reads">buddy-reads</a>, 
